<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Computer_music&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<table class="metadata plainlinks ambox ambox-style" style="">
